Whereas the provinces of Canada, Nova Scotia and New Brunswick have expressed the desire to contract a Federal Union to form one and the same Power ( Dominion ) under the crown of the United Kingdom of the Great Brittany and Ireland, with a constitution based on the same principles as that of the United Kingdom:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Considering further that such a union would have the effect of developing the prosperity of the provinces and promoting the interests of the British Empire:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049\rtlch \ltrch\loch

