Considering further that it is opportune, concurrently with the establishment of the union by authority of parliament, not only to decree the constitution of the legislative power of the Dominion, but also to define the nature of its executive government:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049\rtlch \ltrch\loch

