Ontario Legislature\tab 69.\tab There will be a legislature for Ontario consisting of the Lieutenant Governor and a single chamber called the Legislative Assembly of Ontario.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
